office:meta.dc:title: Grey Elegant
office:meta.dc:description:
Grey Elegant - LibreOffice Impress Template by Ahmad Bayhaqi Saputra
This template is made as an answer to Indonesian LibreOffice Community and Gimpscape ID's call-to-arms to contribute to the 10th anniversary of LibreOffice celebration.
Content Material :
- icons, This template used icons from https://material.io and https://icons8.com/icons - illustrations, This template used illustrations sourced at https://icons8.com/illustrations - Photos, This template used photos sourced at https://unsplash.com
